titleen: Three Hookers and a Philly Cheesesteak
description: Alan tries to grow his business and in doing so inadvertently builds a ponzi scheme. He receives investment money from family members like Berta and Herb and sells them on the idea of his booming chiropractic business. Instead of using the money for his business he pockets it and sits back. He loves being rich. Charlie and Rose continue on with their affair. Gordon the pizza guy delivers pizza to Rose?s house and discovers Rose?s secret. He wants to tell Charlie but doesn?t.
